Class IsFFT

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.graph.property.IsFFT
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Property

    public class IsFFT
extends java.lang.Object
implements Property
    Property class that determines if a diagram can be decomposed by FFT. If it can be decomposed, it also provides the way it decomposed the graph.
